Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Temný jiskřivý kámen destrukce!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kene!
